{"id":768796253,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"10 months, 1 week","timestamp":1659996042,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"20 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/768796253/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"50.2 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int romanToInt(String s) {\n        int sum = 0;\n        for(int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++)\n        {\n            int cur = convert(s.substring(i, i+1));\n            boolean adding = true;\n            int search = 1;\n            boolean notSmaller = true;\n            int pastCur = -1;\n            boolean pastAdd = true;\n            while(adding && i + search < s.length() && notSmaller)\n            {\n                if(pastCur == cur)\n                    notSmaller = false;\n                else if(convert(s.substring(i+ search, i + search + 1)) > cur)\n                    adding = false;\n                else if(convert(s.substring(i+ search, i + search + 1)) < cur)\n                    notSmaller = false;\n                search++;\n            }\n            pastCur = cur;\n            pastAdd = adding;\n            if(adding)\n                sum+= cur;\n            else\n                sum-= cur;\n        }\n        return(sum);\n    }\n    \n    public int convert(String s)\n    {\n        if(s.equals(\"M\"))\n            return(1000);\n        else if (s.equals(\"D\"))\n            return(500);\n        else if (s.equals(\"C\"))\n            return(100);\n        else if(s.equals(\"L\"))\n            return(50);\n        else if(s.equals(\"X\"))\n            return(10);\n        else if(s.equals(\"V\"))\n            return(5);\n        else \n            return(1);\n    }  \n    \n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer","has_notes":false}
